  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve] While you have [Yao Qinglan], [MarineBullmon]:
    Cost 6 \n\n\uFF1CDecode (Lv.6 or lower w/[Aqua]/[Sea Animal]\_in any trait)\uFF1E
